{
  "id": 5863985044914176,
  "name": "Clone into all descendant selectedcontent elements",
  "summary": "Several small changes are being made to edge cases of the selectedcontent element:\n- When multiple selectedcontent elements are put in a select element at the same time, all of them will be kept up to date instead of only the first one in DOM order.\n- Updating the selectedcontent element is deferred when it would run during insertion, removal, or moving steps in order to fix security issues. The update is deferred by using post-insertion steps or microtasks.\n\nThis is a PSA instead of an intent to ship because this only changes invalid cases or edge cases, and the usage of customizable select is still quite low (0.02%).",
